&
Turpin DH (1990) Plant Physiology, Biochemistry and Molecular Biology.  Longman Scientific
&
Technical. 529pp.
3.  Grierson D
&
Covey SN (1998) Plant Molecular Biology, 2nd ed.  Chapman and Hall, New York.  233pp.
4.  Lewin B (1997) Genes VI.  Oxford University Press, Oxford, New York
&
Tokyo.
Lab manual
1.  Draper J, Scott R, Armitage P
&
Walden R (1988) Plant Genetic Transformation and Gene Expression - A Laboratory Manual.  Blackwell Scientific Publication, Oxford, London, Edinburgh, Boston, Palo Alto
&
Melbourne.
2.  Glover DM (1985) DNA Cloning - A Practical Approach, Vols I
&
II. IRL Press, London.
3.  Glover DM (1989) DNA Cloning - A Practical Approach, Vol III. IRL Press, London.
4.  Sambrook J, Fritsch EF
&
Maniatis T (1989) Molecular Cloning - A Laboratory Manual, 2nd ed.  Vols 1, 2
&
3.  Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory Press, New York.
5.  Schuler MA
&
Zielinski RE ( 1989) Methods in Plant Molecular Biology.  Academic Press Inc, San Diego.
6.  Shaw CH (1988) Plant Molecular Biology - A Practical Approach.  IRL Press, Oxford, Washington DC.
7.  Weissbach A
&
Weissbach H (1988) Methods for Plant Molecular Biology.  Academic Press Inc, San Diego.
三、 成績評量方式
期終考試、期末考試與學期報告各佔三分之一。
四、 預修課程
植物生理、生物化學。
