102 10410
The course is aimed at helping students needing help with their English
composition skills. As such, we will focus on the students writing produced
in their current composition courses.
The main areas of grammar to be covered are:
-Verb tenses with some emphasis on the present simple, the present
perfect, the future, the simple past.
-gerunds and infinitives, subject-verb agreement, singular-plural, count and
non-count nouns, reported speech, articles, noun clauses.
