104 17900
This course will elaborate the philosophical significance of the I Ching. It will take hexagrams Qian, Kun and others as examples to clarify their symbolic meaning and important revelation to our daily life. It will also discuss the cosmology, theory of human nature, ethics, and applied philosophy of the Xi Ci Zhuan.
