104 40802
因果關係與統計相關是兩回事，此乃科學上的常識。而如何從統計相關進一步宣稱有因果關係，不僅攸關科學實作，也是科學哲學上的一個重要議題。本課程主要針對「機率」(probability)、「相關」(correlation)以及「因果」(causality)等概念進行哲學性的分析。尤其著重於分析機率因果論(probabilistic theory of causality)在哪些領域上優於其他傳統討論因果關係的理論，並且深入探討此觀點在當代所遭遇到的困難以及可能的解決方案。
</>
<c>
104 40802
This course is managed to read the section of ‘Self-consciousness’ in Hegel’s Phenomenology of Spirit to help the student write his thesis on Hegel. Hegel’s Phenomenology of Spirit reveals the development of consciousness into spirit, and further into Absolute Knowledge. In this process there are moments of ‘Self-consciousness’ in the chapter Die Wahrheit der Gewisheit seiner selbst. The Self-consciousness comes from the consciousness and leads to the reason in the phenomenological development of spirit. The famous dialectics of ‘Lord-slave relationship’ is contained in it.
</>
