107 10402
課程名稱：日語聽講實習
學 分：2學分
授課對象：本校日文系一年級學生
教 材：
1.文化外國語專門學校日本語科編著「輕鬆聽日語1、2」(大新書局)
2.每日聽力日本語五十日課程 初級I、II (大新書局)
課程目標：習得正確的日語發音，習慣日常之日語會話速度，正確掌握會話內容。
授課方式：使用視聽教室設備，修正同學發音，特別是長音、促音、清音、濁音之區別，及鼻音部位、重音等項。其次要求同學比照錄音帶中速度反覆練習，最後針對錄音帶中會話內容發問，已確認同學之聽力，以其達到正確之日語發音、流暢之語調。
Title：Japanese Oral / Audio Training
Credits：2credits
Teaching materials：
1.Primary material：“Listening to Japanese easily1, 2”by Bunka
Institute of Language, published by Shuang-Da
2.Additional material：“Listening to Japanese every day：50days,
Elementary1, 2”published by Dahhsin bookstore
Course description：
※This course is prepared only for the freshmen at the department of Japanese language and literature.
※Aims：In this course, we will learn accurate Japanese pronunciation, acquaint ourselves with natural speed of conversation in daily life, and comprehend the context correctly.
※ Procedure：First of all, with the apparatus in Audio-Visual building, the main purpose is to correct and distinguish different pronunciations, especially the long vowels, geminate, voiceless and voiced consonants. In addition, the nasal and stress will be emphasized.
Secondly, students will be asked to do instant practice and to speak as fast as the demonstration in tape.
The last will be that students have been required to express adviser’s questions according to the context so as to make sure that everyone understands. By doing this, everyone can speak with correct pronunciation and fluency.
</>
