203 34220
本課程為第二部分的基礎無機化學，主要內容包含配位化學、有機金屬化學、生物無機化學。
This course is the second part of the basic inorganic chemistry. It will cover  coordination chemistry, organometallic chemistry, and bioinorganic chemistry.
