<c>
204 20800
This course aims to provide training and experience of field geological survey for undergraduate students.  We plan to focus on topics that are related to some major geological hazards, such as tectonic movement and landslide.  The actual field area will be determined on the basis of the specific topic chosen.  The students are expected to join the field survey and finish a written report of the field work.  The grades will be determined by the participation of the student in the field and the content of the report.
</>
