222 D3320
此課程將會對 "超穎材料"(Metamaterials)這一新研究領域的源起、原理、應用以及最新發展做最深入的介紹，並請修課同學一起參與研討，大綱所列內容都會介紹。
1. Background and introduction to metamaterial
2. The fundamental of Maxwell‘s Equations and plasmonic
3. Negative index metamaterial
4. Chiral metamaterial
5. Metamaterial with artificial magnetism
5. Transformation optics metamaterial
6. Sensor metamaterial
7. Amplifying metamaterial
8. Switchable/reconfigurable metamaterial
9. Nonlinear metamaterial
10. Quantum metamaterial
