222 D5410
The class offers an overview of the most up-to-date optical microscopy and spectroscopy techniques in nanoscale. Three main topics will be covered in the lectures; 1. Super-resolution for bioimaging 2. Plasmonics and near field optics. 3. Optical tracking and dynamics.
