223 D0220
Practical teaching experience in actual laboratory/classroom situations to enhance students’ supervising capability and good quality as would-be teachers/leaders in their professional careers
</>
<c>
223 D0220
1.	Background
2.	Basic Principles
3.	Transmission-line Parameters
4.	Transmission-line Modeling
5.	Transformer Modeling and the Per Unit System
6.	Generator Modeling
</>
