244 M1130
授課教師將在本課程中，介紹恆星的形成、演化，與結束的過程。
第1週		Introduction and Overview
第2週		Thermodynamic Properties of the Stellar Interior (I)
第3週		Thermodynamic Properties of the Stellar Interior (II)
第4週		Nuclear Processes and Burning Stages
第5週		Energy Transport and the Interaction of Radiation and Matter (I)
第6週		Energy Transport and the Interaction of Radiation and Matter (II)
第7週		Star Formation and Evolution (I)
第8週		Star Formation and Evolution (II)
第9週		Midterm Exam
第10週		Structure and Evolution of Low Mass Stars (I)
第11週		Structure and Evolution of Low Mass Stars (II)
第12週		Structure and Evolution of Massive Stars (I)
第13週		Structure and Evolution of Massive Stars (II)
第14週		Stellar Stability, Variable Stars, and Cataclysmic Variables (I)
第15週		Stellar Stability, Variable Stars, and Cataclysmic Variables (II)
第16週		Chemical Evolution — from a Stellar Point of View
第17週		Final Exam
