401 352B0
微生物培養、染色、菌種鑑定、抗生素抑菌效果及反應等操作。包含：Microbes in environment Inoculation of culture media、Simple stain、Gram stain、Action of physical agents on microbes、Action of chemical agents on microbes、Antibiotic sensitivity test---paper disc method、Antibiotic sensitivity test---agar dilution method、Bacteriophages、Staphylococci, Streptococci (demo)、Pneumococci、 Neisseriae (demo)、Bacteriological examination of water (I)、Enterobacteriaceae (I)、Bacteriological examination of water (II)、Enterobacteriaceae (II)、Spore stain、Acid-fast stain、Spirochetes(demo)、Mycoplasma、Fungi、Virological methods (demo)、Outbreak ”(video)
