402 54330
討論口腔顎面區域疾病之診斷及治療與各種手術方法，其中包括口腔顎面區域感染、外傷、先天性畸形、各種良性與惡性病灶之處置，顳顎關節疾病與各種顎面痛症之處理。
THE COURSE IS TO STUDY THE DIAGNOSIS AND TREATMENT OF ORAL AND MAXILLOFACIAL DISEASES, INCLUDING ORAL AND MAXILLOFACIAL INFECTIONS, TRAUMA, CONGENITAL AND ACQUIRED DEFORMITIES, BENIGN AND MALIGNANT LESIONS, TEMPOROMANDIBULAR DISORDERS AND MAXILLOFACIAL PAIN, DENTOALVEOLAR SURGERY, DENTAL IMPLANT AND PREPROSTHETIC SURGERY.
</>
