402 58100
介紹牙科植體之發展,骨整合之生物基礎,植體材料學,生物機械原理,治療計劃,手術過程與技巧,補綴過程與技巧,治療後之長期維持。
Introduce the development of dental implants, the biological basis of osseointegration, implant material science, biomechanical principles, treatment planning, surgical procedure, prosthetic procedure and long term maintenance of implant prosthesis
