422 M6060
美容牙科學是由美學基礎, 牙科美學評估概念與牙科材料之應用及臨床治療考量之縱合課程, 主要是提昇學生之美學素養、牙科美學概念與牙科材料之應用及臨床美容牙科治療考量之課程。本課程之目標旨在引導牙體復形美容牙科研究生由藝術美學入門，建立美學概念，進而對於牙科美學及相關評估與治療有所瞭解。由生活化之美學藝術素養分享、 牙科美學考量之書籍與論文、美容牙科材料之發展與比較、美容牙科治療之論文與臨床病例。
</>
<c>
422 M6080
Esthetic dentistry is based from esthetics, dental esthetic evaluation concept and dental materials applications in clinics. The purpose of the course is to increase the esthetic concept in dentistry and application of dental materials in clinical esthetic dentistry. The course aims for guiding the postgraduate students in Esthetic restoration department to start from the point view of art and build up the concept of esthetics and understand the dental esthetics and related evaluation and treatment. It is a life style esthetic art sharing, regarding the esthetic considered books and papers, comparison of the development of dental esthetic materials, and papers about esthetic dentistry and clinical cases reports.
</>
<c>
422 M6120
本課程針對牙科材料之研發與測試之相關研究進行專題討論,複合樹脂, 嵌體治療, 牙本質黏合劑,電腦3D齒雕,全瓷冠 牙齒美白劑, 牙科雷射, 牙科植體之相關研究主題進行專題討論
</>
<c>
422 M6140
This course is the seminar about the development and related researches of dental materials including composites, materials for inlay/onlay restorations, dentin bonding agents, 3D ceramics, bleaching agents, dental laser and  dental implants. Postgraduate students can have deep understanding of the development and test of dental materials and have right concept about research methods and experimental design.  Students should involve the research topic about these dental materials and propose report and discussion
</>
