Phase I therapy : 25 cases
Medically compromised patients:	5 cases
Gingivectomy/gingivoplasty:10 cases
Flap operation with/without osseous surgery: 100 cases
Mucogingival surgery (FGG, LPF, CPF):10 operations
Bone graft: 20 operations
GTR:	20 operations
Crown lengthening:	10 cases
Hemisection/root resection:	5 operations
Tunneling:5 operations
Apical positioned flap,
vestibuloplasty: 15 operations
Ridge augmentation, GBR:5 cases
Cross-arch temporary splinting	 :5cases
Occlusal adjustment:10 cases Implant and other root submerged procedure: 10 cases
Research project (can be published): optional
˙診療病例必須有完整之資料收集(full documentation)包括：
1.完整牙周病歷表、幻燈片、X光片、口腔牙齒模型，分析病例，就診斷訂定治療計劃及相關科之照會建議。
2.完成牙周病基本治療、口腔衛生教育及口腔衛生監控。
3.治療所需各種牙周手術及重建等後續治療。
4.牙周術後之支持性維護治療。
