THE COURSE REQUIRES DOCTORAL STUDENTS TO SEARCH THE LATEST SCIENTIFIC LITERATURE IN THEIR DISSERTATION RELATED FIELDS, TO PRESENT ORALLY AND TO DISCUSS THE PAPERS WITH PROFESSORS AND OTHER STUDENTS. THE STUDENTS ARE EXPECTED TO ENHANCE THEIR ABILITY TO SET UP EXPERIMENTS AND TO LEARN TO SOLVE TECHNICAL PROBLEMS THROUGH THE DISCUSSION.
