449 M1320
Examination of the basic dendritic cell biology and its applications in medicine and biotechnology by studying updated papers. These contents will lay the foundation for dendritic cell biology, immune regulation of dendritic cell, interaction of dendritic cell with other immune cells, and the application of dendritic cell in many fields.
