453 D0100
腫瘤藥理學
本課程以演講及討論方式進行。授課老師為臨床腫瘤學醫師，以癌症病人實際應用之觀點，講解抗癌藥物在體內作用之機轉及治療目標。學習目標是熟知目前臨床可使用及開發中之抗癌藥物之機轉及應用，進而對轉譯醫學有更深層之認識。
課程大綱
抗癌藥物概論
抗癌藥物發展史
Antimetabolites
Topo isomerase inhibitors
Cell cycle progression and microtubule inhibitors
Alkylating agents and platinum
Antiangiogenesis agents
Tyrosine kinase inhibitors
Antibodies and hormone treatment
Novel anticancer mechanisms
Radiation sensitizers
Multidrug resistance
Drug evaluation: preclinical studies
Drug evaluation: clinical trials, pharmacology aopect
Basic pharma cok
