501 20020
ALMOST ALL OF THE ENGINEERING SKILL PROBLEMS ARE HIGHLY SCIENTIFIC BUT NOT ON WORKMAN LEVEL. MATHEMATIC LANGUAGE IS ESSENTIAL TO DESCRIBE AND DEAL WITH MANY PROBLEMS SO IT IS NEEDED BY ENGINEERING STUDENTS, ESPECIALLY HIGH-CLASS ONES WHO WILL BECOME SENIOR ENGINEERS OR RESEARCHERS THAT CAN SOLVE NEW PROBLEMS.
