501 32020
(一)Introduction
Extremization problem, Classification of Structures , Classification of Loads
(二)Fundamental theory of Elasticity
Stress, Strain, Constitutive Law, Solution Techniques
(三)Energy Methods
Principle of Virtual Displacement, Principle of Virtual Force
(四)Matrix Methods
Direct Stiffness Method, Problems of settlement, temperature
(五)Analysis of Beam
Stiffness Matrix, Equivalent Nodal Forces
(六)Analysis of Frame
(七)Force Method
Determinate Structure, Indeterminate Systems
(八)Introduction to Finite Element Method
Shape Function, Field Problems: heat transfer, fluid mechanics, etc.
</>
