522 U5970
1.	Pole placement control,  (1 week)
2.	Internal modeling principle, (1 week)
3.	LQ control, and Kalman filter,  (2 weeks)
4.	LTR control, and LTR observer, (1 week)
5.	H-infinity control,  (2 weeks)
6.	Repetitive control — internal modeling approach,  (1 week)
7.	Repetitive control — adaptive approach (1 week)
8.	Disturbance observer (2 weeks)
9.	Output feedback sliding mode control for mis-matched uncertainties. (2 weeks)
10.	Disturbance rejection control — nonadaptive approach, (1 weeks)
11.	Disturbance rejection control — adaptive approach(1 weeks)
12.	Feedforward control, and zero-phase error tracking controller.
</>
