(Coatings, Inhibitors, Dealloying )
7. Corrosion phenomenology I
(Environmentally-Induced Cracking)
8. Corrosion phenomenology II
(Atmospheric Corrosion, Oxidation, Cathodic Protection, Rebar Corrosion)
