&
Dynamical Similarity)
9.2： 單獨試驗(Open Water Test)
9.3： 螺槳性能曲線(Propeller Characteristic Curves)
9.4： 空蝕(Cavitation)
10：船體、主機與螺槳(Hull,Main Engine
&
Propeller)
10.1：推進試驗(Model Self-Propulsion Test)
10.2：推進效率因子(Propulsion Factor)
10.3：艉跡流與推減值(Wake Fraction
&
Thrust Deduction Factor)
10.4：馬力預估與餘裕(Power Prediction
&
Sea Margin)
11：螺槳設計(Design of Screw Propeller)
