601 20000
本課程為遺傳學的入門課程，內容以古典遺傳學 (transmission genetics) 基本概念與遺傳之分子基礎的介紹與說明為主，輔以介紹族群遺傳學與數量遺傳學等領域重要的觀念。本課程的授課內容包括：
1. Mendelian inheritance
2. Chromosome theory of Inheritance
3. Extension of Mendelian inheritance
4. Non-Mendelian inheritance
5. Genetic linkage
&
mapping in eukaryotes
6. Genetic transfer and mapping in bacteria and bacteriophages
7. Molecular structure of DNA and RNA
8. DNA replication
9. Gene transcription
&
RNA modification
10. Translation of mRNA
11. Regulation of gene expression
12. Gene mutation
13. Genome organization
&
variations
14. Biotechnology
15. Population genetics
16. Quantitative genetics
</>
