<c>
622 D0450
一、課程內容:
1.	Basic Flow Equation
2.	Local-Equilibrium Solutions
3.	Basic Precipitation/Dissolution Flows
4.	The Local Structure of Precipitation/Dissolution Waves
5.	Non-Equilibrium Precipitation/Dissolution Flows
6.	Reaction-Transport Modeling
7.	Flow Driven Reaction Fronts
8.	Dissipative Structures at Reaction Fronts
9.	Reaction Front Morphology
參考書籍
1.	Ortoleva, P. J., 1994. Geochemical Self-Organization. Oxford University Press,New York, 411pp.
2.	Lake, L. W., S. L. Bryant and A. N. Araque-Marlinez,2002. Geochemistry and Fluid Flow,Elsevier, Amsterdam, 226pp.
成績計算方式
1.作業             20％
2.期中考           40％
3.學期報告         40％
</>
