1.  Draper J, Scott R, Armitage P
&
Walden R (1988) Plant Genetic Transformation and Gene Expression - A Laboratory Manual.  Blackwell Scientific Publication, Oxford, London, Edinburgh, Boston, Palo Alto
&
Melbourne.
