848 M2120
-由於市場競爭與保險管理的強化，成本控制與管理已成為醫療機構一項重要之生存發展課題。課程內容涵蓋醫療機構使用之成本制度、預算制度與績效制度的介紹，以及作業基礎成本制度的應用。
Because of the increases in market competition and the control of insurnace programs, cost control and management has been a critical management issue for the sustainability of a health care organization. Subjects discussed in this course include introductions to various costing systems, budgeting systems, and performance evaluation systems. The applications of activity-based costing to health care organizations are also discussed.
</>
