848 M2290
本課程將引導學生，檢視台灣衛生政策之變遷與醫療產業之變化，並就台灣健保支付制度對醫療機構之影響進行討論，再引用數個醫療機構實際面臨之管理議題或難題，進行個案分析與討論。
This course will guide the students to review the changes in health policy and healthcare industry. Discuss the impact from the newly National Health Insurance Reimbursement System changes. Several real cases will be assigned to students for analysis and discussion.
