了解藥品自研發至上市後整個生命週期風險管理的機制與概況
運用流行病學方法研究藥物使用 包括drug utilization pattern, adherence, prescription quality, comparative effectiveness, safety monitoring, outcome research, health services research 詳細介紹相關方法學 包括meta-analysis; propensity score analysis; case-crossover and case-time-control design; comorbidity score and chronic disease score; interrupted time series design and segmented regression analysis等
</>
