849 U0380
台灣是個老化快速的社會，老化的程度在亞洲僅次於日本。老年醫學，特別是老年預防醫學日益受到重視。本課程旨在使臨床工作者熟悉老年預防醫學的各項議題、使非臨床工作者得見臨床老年醫療的梗概。
Taiwan is a rapidly aging society only second to Japan in Asia. Geriatric Medicine, particularly Geriatric Preventive Medicine, is getting more and more important nowadays. This course aimed to help clinicians familiarize with various issues in Geriatric Preventive Medicine and to help non-clinicians get the basic principles of clinical Geriatric Medicine.
</>
