901 30010
本課程是特別開授給大學部同學在電磁學之後的延伸應用選修課程,介紹天線的物理基礎原理,電磁波的產生及傳播特性,並介紹各種天線型態及其在各種無線通訊系統上的應用。今年度改用新教材,採用近日火紅的網路開放版教課書(可供修課學生免費下載)其主要內容包括:(教師自編大綱)
1.	 Introduction of Antennas and Propagation in Wireless Communications
2.	 Fundamentals of Antennas and System Parameters
3.	 Conductor/Wire Antennas
4.	 Aperture Antennas
5.	 Multiple Antennas for Array and Diversity Applications
6.	 Antenna Technologies for Selected Wireless Systems (RFID, UWB, MIMO)
7.	 Noise Issues and Link Budget in Wireless Communications
8.	 Propagation Topics and Issues
9.	 Selected Antenna Special Topics
