102 83420
This course is designed to help students improve their four skills in English. Various kinds of essays will be studied to improve students' reading ability. Audio-visual materials will be used to enhance students' listening ability. Writing exercises are designed to improve students' writing ability. There will be dialogue practices, discussion sessions, group reports and various presentations to encourage students to speak English.
</>
