H01 05000
In this course we look closely at several Taiwanese films over the past two decades, and through them we intend to understand what prominent phenomena and changes have been taking place in Taiwan’s social culture. Taiwanese films present themselves as various attempts to make conversations with the world that we call Taiwan and live in. This course is expected to help us understand and reflect on Taiwanese social culture by not just watching but also “reading” Taiwanese films.
</>
