409 20200
一.課程內容：
This course will introduce theories of human development, prenatal and neurobehavioral development. The development related to motor, language, visual perceptual and psychosocial functions and play will also be discussed respectively. In addition, the developmental tasks from conception to late adulthood will be introduced. In addition, students will go to a kindergarten to observe the development of children aged 2.5 to 6 years.
二.Grading:
出席：5%
期中考：45%
期末考：50%.
