443 M1512
THIS COURSE IS REQUIRED FOR THE GRADUATE STUDENTS MAJORED IN NEUROSCIENCE, IN BOTH MASTER AND PH.D. PROGRAMS, OF THE GRADUATE INSTITUTE OF PHARMACOLOGY, COLLEGE OF MEDICINE, NATIONAL TAIWAN UNIVERSITY. ANY GRADUATE STUDENTS FROM COLLEGE OF LIFE SCIENCE, COLLEGE OF SCIENCE OR COLLEGE OF MEDICINE IN NATIONAL TAIWAN UNIVERSITY,   WHO ARE INTERESTED IN NEUROSCIENCE DISCIPLINES, ARE ALSO WELCOME. THE STUDENTS TAKING THIS COURSE HAVE TO GIVE A SEMINAR BY PRESENTING A SCIENTIFIC ARTICLE PUBLISHED IN HIGH-RANKING JOURNALS IN THE FIELDS RELEVANT TO NEUROBIOLOGY, NEUORPHYSIOLOGY, NEUROPHARMACOLOGY, PSYCHOLOGY, NEUROLOGY, ANESTHESIOLOGY OR PSYCHIATRY. STUDENTS IN PH.D. PROGRAM ARE REQUESTED TO PRESENT A REVIEW ARTICLE AND THOSE IN MATER PROGRAM PRESENT THE REGULAR PAPERS
