1. OLED device physics
2. Organic materials
3. Process and application of OLED
IV. Liquid crystal Display :
1. Material properties of liquid crystal
2. LCD operation
3. Thin-film transistor (TFT) and low temperature poly-silicon (LTPS) technology
V. Light Emitting Display:
1. Semiconductor light emitting diode (LED) fundamental
2. Material growth and LED fabrication
3. LED based display
VI. Other Displays:
1. CRT, FED
2. Projector
3. Lighting
VII. Company visiting (to be arranged)
