P05 U2010
教導基礎分子生物學之中心教條運作。  期望學生熟悉分子生物基本中心教條。本課程為分子生物學基礎課程，適合大三以上同學修習。課程內容包括：(1) Cells as macromolecular assemblies.(2) DNA as genetic information.(3) Nucleic acids and DNA technology.(4) Mutations and DNA repair.(5) From gene to protein.(6) Prokaryotic gene expression.(7) The eukaryotic genome.(8) Eukaryotic gene expression.(9) Cell growth, cancer and development.
